cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.IR. 

The paper is about an image annotation software for image segmentation tasks, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The software also includes features such as painting and erasing, which are related to graphics and multimedia (cs.GR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the software can handle multi-class masks, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
